    <bodyText><![CDATA[
      
           <tags ms.service="hdinsight" ms.date="09/30/2015" wacn.date="11/27/2015"></tags> <!-- BEGIN: Product-Detail-TopBanner -->
            <div class="common-banner col-top-banner" data-config="{'backgroundColor':'#e3f4ff', 'backgroundImage':'//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/hd_insight.png','imageHeight':'auto'}">
                <div class="common-banner-image">
                    <div class="common-banner-title">
                        <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/hdinsight@2x.png" />
                        <h2><span>HDInsight</span></h2>
                        <h4>The only fully-managed cloud-based Hadoop product makes big data understandable and affordable.</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_hd_trial">Apply for trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="home_hd_pia">Purchase now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- END: Product-Detail-TopBanner --> <!-- BEGIN: Pricing calculator -->
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
				<p>Users can select different configurations according to their specific requirements:</p>
				<ul>
				<li>Hadoop cluster should select two head nodes and at least one data node simultaneously</li>
				<li>HBase cluster should select two control servers and at least one region server and three primary/ZooKeeper nodes simultaneously</li>
				<li>Storm cluster should select two Nimbus nodes and at least one supervisor server and three ZooKeeper nodes simultaneously</li>
				<li>Spark cluster should select two head nodes and at least one work process node simultaneously</li>
				</ul>				
				
				<!-- <p>R Server 的边缘节点为非必选项，如果选择会产生 R Server 附加费，附加费的内核数为头节点、数据节点和 R Server 边缘节点的总和。</p> -->
				
				
				<div id="calculator" data-service="hdinsight-windows-hadoop-head hdinsight-windows-hadoop-data hdinsight-windows-hbase-head hdinsight-windows-hbase-region hdinsight-windows-hbase-zookeeper hdinsight-windows-storm-nimbus hdinsight-windows-storm-supervisor hdinsight-windows-storm-zookeeper hdinsight-linux-hadoop-head hdinsight-linux-hadoop-data hdinsight-linux-hbase-head hdinsight-linux-hbase-region hdinsight-linux-hbase-zookeeper hdinsight-linux-storm-nimbus hdinsight-linux-storm-supervisor hdinsight-linux-storm-zookeeper hdinsight-linux-spark-head hdinsight-linux-spark-worker data-transferenter data-transfer support" data-addService=""></div>

                <!-- BEGIN: Pricing calculator Sidebar-->                      
                <div class="sidebar-win calculator empty hide">
                    <div class="control">
                        <a href="#" class="close" id="closeCalculator"></a>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="calcul-list">
                        <span class="nothing">You haven’t yet selected your price estimation service. Please add it by adjusting the amount on the left-hand side.</span>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="summary">
                        <div class="total">
                            Total price
                            <p>
                                <span class="num">RMB&#160;0.00</span> <span class="unit">/month</span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn-group">
                            <a class="calcul-btn buy" href="/pricing/pia/" id="sidebarWinCalculBuy">Go to purchase</a> <a class="calcul-btn-white export" href="#" id="sidebarWinCalculExport">Export list</a> <a class="calcul-btn-white reset" href="#" id="sidebarWinCalculReset">Reset</a>
                        </div>
                        <p class="summary-text">
                            Still hesitating? <a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="sidebarWinCalculTry">Try</a> these functions first.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
             
                <!-- start calculator modal -->
                <div class="preload">
                    <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/img/right.png">
                </div>
                <div class="modal modal-calculator hide">
                    <div class="container">
                        <a href="#" class="close" id="closeCalculatorModal"></a>
                        <p>We will add service items selected on different pages to the combined calculation in the right-hand list. You can manually delete or clear items.</p>
                        <span class="checkbox-rect"></span>Don’t prompt again <a class="btn btn-continue" href="#">I’ve got it</a>
                        </div>
                </div>
                <!-- end calculator modal --> <!-- start calculator shopinglist template -->
                <script type="text/template" id="templPricingShopingList">
                    <% _.each(shopingList, function(item){%>
                    <li class="calcul-item">
                        <img src="<%= item.logoUrl %>">
                        <a class="delete" href="#"></a>
                        <div class="info">
                            <div class="name">
                                <span class="short" title="<%= item.name %>"><%= item.name %></span>
                                <% if(item.name.length > 10) { %>
                                <span>...</span>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                            <span class="type">
                                <% _.each(item.details, function(detail){ %>
                                <%= detail  %>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                <% }) %>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="time">
                            <%= item.number %><%= item.unit %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail">
                            <div class="price">
                                <span class="num">￥<%= item.currentMoney %></span>
                                <span class="unit">/月</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <% }) %>
                    <% if(shopingList.length == 0){ %>
                    <span class="nothing">您还没有选择要估算价格的服务，调整左边数量进行添加</span>
                    <% } %>
                </script>
                <!-- end calculator shopinglist template --> <!-- start calculator animation layer -->
                <div class="anima-calculator hide">
                    +1
                </div>
                <!-- end calculator animation layer -->
                <div class="azsidebar"></div>  
                <!-- END: Pricing calculator Sidebar-->                  
            </div>
            <!-- END: Pricing calculator --> <!--BEGIN: Support and service code chunk--> &lt;?UMBRACO_MACRO chunkpath="production" chunkname="production-bottom-banner" macroAlias="blankCodeChunk" />  <!--END: Support and service code chunk-->               
    
    ]]></bodyText>
    <pageTitle>Pricing Calculator - HDInsight | Azure</pageTitle>
