    <metaKeywords>Azure, Microsoft Cloud, HDInsight, price estimation, Hadoop, hosting, Analysis Services, big data, 1 RMB Trial</metaKeywords>
    <metaDescription><![CDATA[Estimate the Azure HDInsight usage costs for your solution. You can select whatever services are required, along with their different types, levels, configurations, and instances. You can view the unit price and total price easily and estimate the required costs. You can also export lists for easy quotes. A 1 RMB Trial gets you RMB 1,500 in service credits. You can also make a direct purchase and become a Pay-in-advance Azure customer to enjoy a service level agreement of up to 99.99%.]]></metaDescription>
    <urlDisplayName>Pricing Calculator - HDInsight</urlDisplayName>
  </TextpageLeftNav>
</localize>
